OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome sunny spells and patchy cloud
OL,7,Faround to start the evening. Staying
OL,8,Fdry overnight with long clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Mild with light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FBecoming warm or very warm on
OL,12,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,13,Falthough this may turn hazy at times.
OL,14,FCloudy and mild overnight with a risk
OL,15,Fof showers.
